instructions:
the increment button should be attached to pin 6 and the
decrement button should be attached to pin 7.  The LED
pins should be connected to pins 9-13 with the order being
red red green red red.
use the provided makefile to compile and put the code onto the arduino
use make in the terminal to create a compiled version of the code
and use make uplaod to upload the code to the arduino.

